csv_post_post: The Minitel is a Videotex online service accessible through the telephone lines, and is considered one of the world's most successful pre-World Wide Web online services.
csv_comment_1_content: Wow, I have never heard about such service.
csv_comment_2_content: From its early days, users could make online purchases, make train reservations, check stock prices, search the telephone directory, and chat in a similar way to that now made possible by the Internet.
